flowchart LR
    subgraph Sources [Data Sources]
        CSV[CSV Files]
        SQL[SQL Databases]
    end

    subgraph Storage [State & Schema Storage]
        Schema[(Schema Truth)]
        SQLite[(SQLite State DB)]
    end

    subgraph Pipeline [Tripwire Verification Pipeline]
        Ingest[Ingestion & Normalization]
        BiEncoder[Bi-Encoder Gate]
        CrossEncoder[Cross-Encoder Gate]
        Decision[Decision Engine]
        Alerts[Alerting & Logging]
    end

    subgraph Target [Target Systems]
        ClearedDB[(Cleared Data Store)]
    end

    subgraph Actors [Users & Stakeholders]
        Operator[Data Operator / Maintainer]
        Stakeholder[IT Security & Business Owners]
    end

    CSV -->|raw structured data| Ingest
    SQL -->|raw structured data| Ingest
    Schema -->|validation schema| Ingest

    Ingest -->|normalized data chunks| BiEncoder
    BiEncoder -->|candidate matches & scores| CrossEncoder
    CrossEncoder -->|high-precision verification scores| Decision

    Decision <-->|read/write state under concurrency limits| SQLite
    
    Decision -->|confidence >= threshold| ClearedDB
    
    Decision -->|confidence < threshold / uncertainty| Alerts
    Alerts -->|loud failure alert & logs| Operator
    Alerts -->|audit logs & reports| Stakeholder
    
    Operator -->|diagnose & calibrate thresholds| Decision
    Operator -->|manual reconciliation via runbooks| SQLite